edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database

Class PopulationStorageDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database.PopulationStorageDB

  • public class PopulationStorageDB
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is based on class PopulationStorage. However attributes are NOT static.
    Note:
    If the population is active, Use the username of the online instructor accessing it.
    Otherwise: Use the username of the creator of the selected population.
    Data can be read either from temporal database (HerdWebDisplay.TEMPORAL) or persistent database (HerdWebDisplay.PERSISTENT).
